{"tid":500912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong Watch: 歐盟議會中的重要報告譴責中國干涉香港內政","createTime":"2017-12-16T09:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T15:35:23.000Z","uid":63669,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9913fbe0deea3d1b30022c3ebe286dfbf4763d8e","tid":500912,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"歐盟議會中的重要報告譴責中國干涉香港內政。 <a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2017/12/16/major-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fall-posts%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2Fmajor-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ca07495f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2017/12/16/major-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs</a><br />\n<br />\n香港觀察董事會主席本尼迪克特&middot;羅傑斯說：&ldquo;我很高興看到歐洲議會對於香港自治的重要性的重要肯定。歐盟和更廣泛的國際社會必須繼續保護香港的&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;，並在香港的人權和自由受到破壞時大聲疾呼。這份報告為歐洲理事會提供了重要的政策建議，我希望安理會採取行動保護香港的自主權。"},{"pid":"79753af66def0a53067ce8e34efba43433719ced","tid":500912,"uid":26506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐盟議會中的重要報告譴責中國干涉香港內政。 <a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2017/12/16/major-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fall-posts%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2Fmajor-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs&d=WzhYenQXNUg8a2tZG0UdSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ca07495f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2017/12/16/major-eu-parliament-report-condemns-chinese-interference-in-hong-kongs-internal-affairs</a><br />\n<br />\n香港觀察董事會主席本尼迪克特&middot;羅傑斯說：&ldquo;我很高興看到歐洲議會對